			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Similar to O'keils radiation of the Wizard.  Any creature hitting you will take some damage for it.  The nice thing about this is if it is cast on your tank, the creature's anger meter will go focus on the tank becuase the creature thinks that it is the tank that is doing the damage on it, not at you for having cast the spell on the tank.
			</font>
	
