		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			This spell has been changed.  Now it is only self cast, and must be researched.  Still does 6 points to anything hitting you though.  You will also need a component to use it. A pearl.  Yes a pearl is worth 3 plat to a merchant, but the spell does not use the pearl up.  So if you keep one pearl in your inventory, you can cast this spell to your hearts content.  Bad thing is, at upper levels, if your getting hit at all, your already dead...Some people love this spell, some hate it.  I have seen no inbetween.
			</font>
	
