	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			This is good for kiting.  <BR>
This is how it works: Pull with Engulfing Darkness, if resisted, sic pet to buy you time to get the spell successfully on the creature.<BR>
Back the pet off and attack creature, who will aggro you.  Start running, and get off Heat Blood and Heart Flutter, renew Engulfing Darkness if necessary.<BR>
The keyto this is, is that when you melee the creature, and it is hit by Banshee Aura, it will piss at you, and ignore your pet, regardless.<BR>
Then you have the creature following you, taking  40 damage a round DoT (11+17+12), and getting wailed on by your pet following behind.
			</font>
	
		</td>
	</tr>
	
